This paper is about improving the security of image manipulation detection, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of Support Vector Machines (SVM) for classification, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of attacks on image manipulation detectors, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
